        }
      }
    },
    "Natural Scrolling follows the macOS setting for trackpads and Magic Mouse. Reverse Mouse Scrolling is handled by Cyclope and affects physical mouse wheel events only." : {
      "comment" : "Footer for the Scroll Direction settings section.",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Natural Scrolling follows the macOS setting for trackpads and Magic Mouse. Reverse Mouse Scrolling is handled by Cyclope and affects physical mouse wheel events only."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "자연스러운 스크롤은 트랙패드와 Magic Mouse에 적용되는 macOS 설정을 따릅니다. 마우스 스크롤 방향 반전은 Cyclope에서 처리하며 물리적인 마우스 휠 이벤트에만 적용됩니다."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Natural Scrolling is the macOS setting for trackpads and Magic Mouse. Wheel mouse reversal is handled by Cyclope and affects physical mouse wheel events only. Some mouse utilities, including Logitech Options+, can emit trackpad-like scrolling and may ignore wheel mouse reversal." : {
      "comment" : "Footer for the Scroll Direction settings section.",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Natural Scrolling is the macOS setting for trackpads and Magic Mouse. Wheel mouse reversal is handled by Cyclope and affects physical mouse wheel events only. Some mouse utilities, including Logitech Options+, can emit trackpad-like scrolling and may ignore wheel mouse reversal."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "자연스러운 스크롤은 트랙패드와 Magic Mouse에 적용되는 macOS 설정입니다. 마우스 휠 방향 반전은 Cyclope에서 처리하며 물리적인 마우스 휠 이벤트에만 적용됩니다. Logitech Options+ 등 일부 마우스 유틸리티는 트랙패드와 유사한 스크롤 이벤트를 내보내 마우스 휠 방향 반전이 적용되지 않을 수 있습니다."
          }
        }
      }
    },
